This repo contains dvipdf and supporting files.

-----------------------------

Put *.pfb files from the following archives to this directory:

https://www.ams.org/arc/tex/amsfonts.zip
https://mirrors.ctan.org/fonts/ps-type1/cm-super.zip

-----------------------------

To correctly copy/search quoteleft, quoteright and minus,
apply the following changes to ghostscript source (version
does not matter, so use latest):

In the end of function pdf_simple_font_needs_ToUnicode change
'return false' to 'return true'

In Resource/Decoding/Unicode change:

-16#0027  quotesingle SP050000
+16#0027  quotesingle SP050000 quoteright

-16#002D  hyphen      SP100000 hyphen-minus hyphenminus
+16#002D  hyphen      SP100000 hyphen-minus hyphenminus minus

-16#0060  grave       SD130000
+16#0060  grave       SD130000 quoteleft

-16#2018  quoteleft   SP190000 quotesinglleft
+16#2018              SP190000 quotesinglleft

-16#2019  quoteright  SP200000 quotesinglright
+16#2019              SP200000 quotesinglright

-16#2212  minus

Build ghostscript:

./configure --prefix=/usr/local/ghostscript
make
make install

To see the effect of this, add -dCompressFonts=false to ps2pdf,
open pdf file via 'less' and search CMap
